            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 max-w-sm mx-auto leading-relaxed">Your personal assistant for effortless task management and a productive day. </p>
           
        </div>

        <div class="relative bg-white bg-opacity-100 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-blue-100 w-full transform transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out hover:scale-[1.01] square-card">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 mb-4 tracking-tight"> Project <span style="color:darkgreen">Management</span></h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 max-w-sm mx-auto leading-relaxed"> Track every step of your project effortlessly. </p>

        </div>

        <div class="relative bg-white bg-opacity-100 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-blue-100 w-full transform transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out hover:scale-[1.01] square-card">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4 tracking-tight"> Task <span style="color:crimson"> Management </span></h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 max-w-sm mx-auto leading-relaxed"> Track your tasks and view priority level for effective time management. </p>

        </div>
