            <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">Dash <span style="color:plum"> Boards </span></h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 max-w-sm mx-auto leading-relaxed"> All your tasks and projects in one central place. </p>

        </div>

        <div class="relative bg-white bg-opacity-100 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-blue-100 w-full transform transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out hover:scale-[1.01] square-card">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">Report <span style="color:tomato">Dashboard</span></h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 max-w-sm mx-auto leading-relaxed">View your progress stats in real time. </p>

        </div>

        <div class="relative bg-white bg-opacity-100 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-blue-100 w-full transform transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out hover:scale-[1.01] square-card">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4 tracking-tight">Our <span style="color:mediumaquamarine">Promise</span></h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 max-w-sm mx-auto leading-relaxed"> The stress of missing deadlines is out of the window. Keep in the loop on what needs to be done and when. </p>

        </div>
    </section>



</body>

